{
  "chapter": 89,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙化名董匡与龙阳君并骑出城前往藏军谷。途中龙阳君分析纪嫣然真正爱的是项少龙，并表示要盯紧纪嫣然以挖出项少龙。他评价项少龙是不世人才，但因立场对立必须将其杀死，同时指出吕不韦和项少龙行踪泄露可能有诈。项少龙对龙阳君的敏锐观察力暗自心惊。队伍进入山峡时项少龙凭直觉感到危机，果然峡内伏兵四起，弩箭齐发。项少龙搂着龙阳君滚入树林，率焦旭等残余亲卫浴血奋战。他展现出特种部队训练的惊人耐力和气脉，一路杀出重围，最终带众人跳入河中借水遁走。回邯郸后赵穆和乐乘在城门迎接，龙阳君对项少龙舍命相救感激不已。善柔、乌果、田氏姊妹迎他回府，项少龙已猜到偷袭龙阳君的幕后主使。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何不见贵仆龙善？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "内人还是第一趟来到大城市，购物兴浓，没有人护持总是不大妥当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "李园视董兄为头号情敌，实在是弄错了目标，教人发噱。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "君上何有此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "纪嫣然真正看上的人是项少龙。唉！嫣然自己或者没有察觉，她看少龙的眼神与看其他人时有很大的分别。在那时她可能仍不知道自己爱上项少龙，但我已肯定地知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我才不信纪嫣然和项少龙间没有密约，只要盯紧纪嫣然，终可由她身上把项少龙挖出来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "君上不是要对付纪才女吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我一直视她为红颜知己，她投向项少龙是自然不过的一回事。董先生尚未见过项少龙，这人确是不世的人才，无论谈吐见地和襟胸气概均独特出众，本人若非与他站在敌对的立场，招揽他还来不及，但现在却必须不择手段，务要把他杀死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "我虽然自知没有得到纪才女的希望，可是却也觉得她颇看得起我老董。嘿！凭君上的眼光，她看我的目光比之看项少龙如何？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她的确很看得起你，问题在她是个相当死心眼的人，绝不会像赵雅般见异思迁，项少龙有先入为主的优势，你和李园只好死去这条心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "事情看来还未绝望，有君上这么厉害的人对付项少龙，他能活的日子应屈指可数了，那时纪才女不是要再行挑选对象吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事实早证明所有低估项少龙的人，最后莫不饮恨收场。无论赵人如何布置，我仍深信项少龙有神不知鬼不觉潜入邯郸的本领。以吕不韦和项少龙的狡猾，怎会任由行踪给秦国的敌对派系泄露出来，其中定是有诈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙最重要的仇人有三个，就是孝成王、赵穆和郭纵，一天项少龙仍在，他们三人恐怕难以安寝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "项少龙与君上是否亦有过节呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我开路！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生想清楚本君那天的说话了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "为何贵侍卫们仍未回来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小心点总是好的！本君对董先生的小心谨慎非常欣赏。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生有没有想过纵横战场，创一番男儿的不朽事业？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "我除养马外，对兵法一窍不通，拼拼蛮力或尚可将就，怎能统领三军，驰骋沙场？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生不用自谦，只看贵属训练有素，悍不畏死，便知先生是天生将才，否则田单哪会如此顾忌你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快掉头！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跳下去！这是我们唯一逃生的机会。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若非董先生舍命相救，我如今恐难有命再见两位了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有没有见到项少龙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_le_cheng",
      "text": "看来不大像是项少龙，不过当时形势混乱之极，我们只顾着逃走，藉河而遁，根本未有机会看清楚敌人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已派出精兵封锁所有要道，搜索远近山头，希望可以有好消息禀知君上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "早知我陪你去！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人干的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让我醒过来后向你们详说一切好吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    }
  ],
